\size footnotesize
Note: This figure displays the network of inventor flows between NAICS 3-digit
 sectors and the knowledge markets resulting from the application of the
 Louvain community detection algorithm.
 Lines denote inventor transitions, with width proportional to the effective
 undirected inventor flow between sectors.
 Nodes represent NAICS 3-digit sectors.
 Black lines depict flows within knowledge markets, while gray lines transitions
 between communities.
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

